            <title><![CDATA[关系型数据库 vs 非关系型数据库]]></title>
            <link>https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql</link>
            <guid>https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql</guid>
            <pubDate>Sat, 20 Jan 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[概述]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="概述">概述<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E6%A6%82%E8%BF%B0" class="hash-link" aria-label="概述的直接链接" title="概述的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>数据库是后端开发的核心组件。主要分为两大类：关系型数据库（RDBMS）和非关系型数据库（NoSQL）。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="关系型数据库">关系型数据库<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="关系型数据库的直接链接" title="关系型数据库的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="特点">特点<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9" class="hash-link" aria-label="特点的直接链接" title="特点的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>结构化数据</strong>：使用表存储数据</li>
<li class=""><strong>SQL 查询语言</strong>：强大的查询能力</li>
<li class=""><strong>事务支持</strong>：ACID 特性</li>
<li class=""><strong>数据完整性</strong>：外键约束</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="常见产品">常见产品<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81" class="hash-link" aria-label="常见产品的直接链接" title="常见产品的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<table><thead><tr><th>数据库</th><th>特点</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>MySQL</td><td>开源最流行</td></tr><tr><td>PostgreSQL</td><td>功能最强大</td></tr><tr><td>Oracle</td><td>企业级应用</td></tr><tr><td>SQL Server</td><td>微软生态</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="使用场景">使用场景<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF" class="hash-link" aria-label="使用场景的直接链接" title="使用场景的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">金融系统</li>
<li class="">电商订单管理</li>
<li class="">用户管理系统</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="非关系型数据库">非关系型数据库<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E9%9D%9E%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="非关系型数据库的直接链接" title="非关系型数据库的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="特点-1">特点<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E7%89%B9%E7%82%B9-1" class="hash-link" aria-label="特点的直接链接" title="特点的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>灵活的数据模型</strong>：无需预定义表结构</li>
<li class=""><strong>高性能</strong>：支持高并发读写</li>
<li class=""><strong>水平扩展</strong>：易于分布式部署</li>
<li class=""><strong>多样的数据模型</strong></li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="常见产品-1">常见产品<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81-1" class="hash-link" aria-label="常见产品的直接链接" title="常见产品的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<table><thead><tr><th>类型</th><th>产品</th><th>用途</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>文档</td><td>MongoDB</td><td>内容管理</td></tr><tr><td>键值</td><td>Redis</td><td>缓存、会话</td></tr><tr><td>列式</td><td>Cassandra</td><td>大数据分析</td></tr><tr><td>图</td><td>Neo4j</td><td>社交网络</td></tr></tbody></table>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="使用场景-1">使用场景<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E5%9C%BA%E6%99%AF-1" class="hash-link" aria-label="使用场景的直接链接" title="使用场景的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">日志分析</li>
<li class="">实时数据处理</li>
<li class="">缓存层</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="如何选择">如何选择？<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9" class="hash-link" aria-label="如何选择？的直接链接" title="如何选择？的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="选择关系型数据库当">选择关系型数据库当：<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E5%BD%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="选择关系型数据库当：的直接链接" title="选择关系型数据库当：的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">需要复杂查询</li>
<li class="">数据结构相对固定</li>
<li class="">事务处理必不可少</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="选择非关系型数据库当">选择非关系型数据库当：<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9%E9%9D%9E%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB%E5%9E%8B%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E5%BD%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="选择非关系型数据库当：的直接链接" title="选择非关系型数据库当：的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class="">数据量巨大</li>
<li class="">需要高并发</li>
<li class="">数据结构灵活多变</li>
</ul>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="总结">总结<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/20/sql-vs-nosql#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="总结的直接链接" title="总结的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>现代应用通常是混合使用两种数据库，取长补短。</p>
<hr>
<p>喜欢本文的话，欢迎留言讨论！💬</p>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>数据库</category>
            <category>后端</category>
            <category>基础</category>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[后端开发入门指南]]></title>
            <link>https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started</link>
            <guid>https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[什么是后端开发？]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="什么是后端开发">什么是后端开发？<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E6%98%AF%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91" class="hash-link" aria-label="什么是后端开发？的直接链接" title="什么是后端开发？的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>后端开发是指服务器端的开发，负责处理数据存储、业务逻辑和 API 接口等工作。与前端不同，后端用户通常看不到，但却是整个应用的核心。</p>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="后端开发的核心技能">后端开发的核心技能<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#%E5%90%8E%E7%AB%AF%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%9A%84%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E6%8A%80%E8%83%BD" class="hash-link" aria-label="后端开发的核心技能的直接链接" title="后端开发的核心技能的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="1-编程语言">1. 编程语言<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#1-%E7%BC%96%E7%A8%8B%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80" class="hash-link" aria-label="1. 编程语言的直接链接" title="1. 编程语言的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>常见的后端语言包括：</p>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>Java</strong> - 企业级应用广泛使用</li>
<li class=""><strong>Python</strong> - 简单易学，适合快速开发</li>
<li class=""><strong>Go</strong> - 高性能，适合微服务</li>
<li class=""><strong>Node.js</strong> - JavaScript 运行环境，前端开发者友好</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="2-数据库">2. 数据库<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#2-%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="2. 数据库的直接链接" title="2. 数据库的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<ul>
<li class=""><strong>关系型数据库</strong>：MySQL、PostgreSQL</li>
<li class=""><strong>非关系型数据库</strong>：MongoDB、Redis</li>
</ul>
<h3 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="3-api-设计">3. API 设计<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#3-api-%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1" class="hash-link" aria-label="3. API 设计的直接链接" title="3. API 设计的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h3>
<p>RESTful API 是目前最常用的接口设计风格：</p>
<div class="language-javascript codeBlockContainer_Ckt0 theme-code-block" style="--prism-color:#393A34;--prism-background-color:#f6f8fa"><div class="codeBlockContent_QJqH"><pre tabindex="0" class="prism-code language-javascript codeBlock_bY9V thin-scrollbar" style="color:#393A34;background-color:#f6f8fa"><code class="codeBlockLines_e6Vv"><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token comment" style="color:#999988;font-style:italic">// 示例：RESTful API 设计</span><span class="token plain"></span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token constant" style="color:#36acaa">GET</span><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">api</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">users        # 获取用户列表</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token constant" style="color:#36acaa">GET</span><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">api</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">users</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain">id    # 获取单个用户</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token constant" style="color:#36acaa">POST</span><span class="token plain">   </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">api</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">users        # 创建用户</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token constant" style="color:#36acaa">PUT</span><span class="token plain">    </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">api</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">users</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain">id    # 更新用户</span><br></span><span class="token-line" style="color:#393A34"><span class="token plain"></span><span class="token constant" style="color:#36acaa">DELETE</span><span class="token plain"> </span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">api</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token plain">users</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">/</span><span class="token operator" style="color:#393A34">:</span><span class="token plain">id    # 删除用户</span><br></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="学习路线建议">学习路线建议<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#%E5%AD%A6%E4%B9%A0%E8%B7%AF%E7%BA%BF%E5%BB%BA%E8%AE%AE" class="hash-link" aria-label="学习路线建议的直接链接" title="学习路线建议的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<ol>
<li class=""><strong>选择一个后端语言</strong>：推荐 Python 或 Node.js</li>
<li class=""><strong>掌握数据库基础</strong>：从 MySQL 开始</li>
<li class=""><strong>学习 RESTful API 设计</strong></li>
<li class=""><strong>了解微服务概念</strong></li>
<li class=""><strong>实践项目</strong>：完成一个完整的 CRUD 应用</li>
</ol>
<h2 class="anchor anchorTargetStickyNavbar_Vzrq" id="总结">总结<a href="https://oo-ok-kk.github.io/tech-blog/blog/2024/01/15/backend-getting-started#%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93" class="hash-link" aria-label="总结的直接链接" title="总结的直接链接" translate="no">​</a></h2>
<p>后端开发需要扎实的编程基础和系统设计能力。建议初学者先选择一门语言，深入学习，然后通过项目实践来巩固知识。</p>
<hr>
<p>Happy Coding! 🚀</p>]]></content:encoded>
            <category>后端</category>
            <category>入门</category>
            <category>教程</category>
        </item>
